from 2011-02-04

simple servlet-skeleton, worked with/for

with :
java 1.6.0 update 23 or after
maven 3.0.2 (2.2.1 will work, maybe...)
git (msysgit + tortoisegit)

for :
eclipse 3.6 for java ee, WTP
tomcat 6.0.32 (NOT tested in tomcat 7) 

etc :
should avoid commons-logging
should avoid getting parameters from GET request now, too hard to get right

should edit tomcat server.xml for UTF-8 string filter - URIEncoding="UTF-8"
(see http://wiki.apache.org/tomcat/FAQ/CharacterEncoding)